{"tid":1378606,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.28 事後檢討","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T16:28:27.000Z","uid":44870,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe3f771bd74ef790e3857e83433940d1c89339f","tid":1378606,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:14:58.000Z","msg":"眾所周知今日好多前線俾人生擒, 最主要係大量速龍同一時間衝出黎, 大家怯場,本能反應自然縮, 要成功必須克服呢個當前難題, 請各位手足拋低各種可行方法.<br />\n<br />\n我個人認為對付速龍,<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【和理非】嘅裝備升級</span></span></strong>可以幫到前線爭取更多時間, 所需要嘅其實好簡單, 就係<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一支強力電筒或者激光電筒</span></span></strong></strong>, 照住班速龍:<br />\n1. 可以俾前線認清速龍同埋佢地所在位置;<br />\n2. 可以用強光遮擋速龍視線, 起碼可以阻礙佢地迅速推進;<br />\n3. 遠攻絕對安全, 裝備易購入而且冇攻擊性絕對唔會俾狗咬;<br />\n<br />\n起碼可以幫前線爭取多幾秒鐘撤退時間, 甚至可以配合前線 e.g 波子陣, 大大保障前線義士嘅安全.而且和理非通常企係中後排, 撤退時視線可以keep住望住班差佬, 所以呢份筍工絕對適合你地."},{"pid":"af82448335ffc1a6fe706f9699eb5e1408c99f36","tid":1378606,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:17:27.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉"},{"pid":"d832b165d2ae3d6070008ffa25f66263ceb9b2a5","tid":1378606,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18344d4e42841524f708663e92deb27a57bc2b2c","tid":1378606,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64838c173d41a630ac5707da02f8b67efd43eff3","tid":1378606,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/reu36X3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Freu36X3.gif&h=2ae11e1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cb3304b40bd6c340f5a4e8496b1a9ca19d916c0","tid":1378606,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64838c173d41a630ac5707da02f8b67efd43eff3","